><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持"},{"pid":"7bb2c5654bde4edb41261513505af33c98f0f754","tid":1713881,"uid":206557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"哇 邊個話香港啲特技唔真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb3cb74e3bf4f4501136b9a2fae9458dc3f846a","tid":1713881,"uid":273188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:05:54.000Z","msg":"（緊急）點解之前死都唔肯停課，昨天停曬八大，之後就暴力清場，好明顯政府認為滅左你大學生，事件就會完，<br />\n所有其它大學要作最壞打算，準備可以立即徹離，唔可以比人圍困<br />\n對無人性的林鄭來說，唔好誤以為停課係為你地安全着想，佢係想暴力清場。<br />\n仲有，有消息內地生徹走，好明顯為屠殺鋪路<br />\n必須推上國際，要話比世界聽&ldquo;天安門事件&rdquo;又即將發生，仲要係警察想走入八大，消滅整個世代的大學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712238</a>"},{"pid":"66fa8824b25fe429e1685c8c499313b21c9a6d16","tid":1713881,"uid":285716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2c11cdc128b2a5319cf52f3f5ba6fabbb6f963","tid":1713881,"uid":311835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:24:27.000Z","msg":"Michael Bay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86743cae64f6e664f17cb4e7b6317581694c8898","tid":1713881,"uid":56647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:30:20.000Z","m